          "reviewBody": "The best school ever in this world which has alot of memories of mine. From Lkg to HSC this years where the best years of my life.I m still in touch with my friends n teachers who thought me what is life all about the best school with best teachers .I will always miss this place and it has a  special place in my heart❤️",
