          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Husain Najam"
          },
          "datePublished": "2020-08-31",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Pride of Dear Old Bombay, Ever and Ever New was the anthem of our school. Studied here from LKG until SSC in 2002. Can easily say they were the best years of my life. From Mr Mulla to each and every teacher in the school it was the best when I studied there. All the school memories and my friends we are all still in touch although in different parts of the world. Best location in Bombay with Huge Vintage classrooms and benches 😃. You get the best Bhatt Vada Pav here in Bombay and also samosa ragda. Loved my school life and I miss it more then anything. May god give this school its old glory back soon.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
